::DevilDuer::

DevilDuer grins. "Good!"

"Zardus, I have two new recruits that also want to help with the mission," he 
says into his comm.

"Good," Zardus' voice replies, "Meet up with Reptilica and Bloodystrike, they 
have the coordinates."

DevilDuer nods, walking off toward the lab and motioning Treadshot to follow 
him.
